{% comment %}
  PRNTD — Immersive Homepage
  Rebrand v3 — February 2026
  Inspired by: Juun.J Persona, Acne Studios, The Row
  
  Structure:
  1. Full-screen hero with circular reveal interaction
  2. Campaign statement — massive typography
  3. Highlights — asymmetric editorial grid
  4. Brand philosophy — manifesto section
  5. All Looks — collection preview
  6. Archive — previous collections carousel
  7. Footer — full utility footer
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} ============================================================
   SECTION 1: IMMERSIVE HERO (unchanged)
   ============================================================ {% endcomment %}

